{
  "version": "SOC 2 (AICPA Trust Services Criteria 2017, with 2022 updates)",
  "description": "SOC 2 Trust Services Criteria covering 5 categories: Common Criteria (Security), Availability, Processing Integrity, Confidentiality, and Privacy.",
